# S06-T02: Stream Diagnostics Section

## Objective
UI panel rendering stream stats from S02-T07 (bitrate, FPS, jitter, drops, latency).

## Acceptance Criteria
- `<StreamDiagnostics>` section inside DebugPanel.
- Displays: source type, resolution, codec (where known), bitrate, FPS, jitter, drop %, latency.
- Mini-graphs for bitrate + FPS (using S03-T04 Graph component, 60s window).
- Quality grade indicator (cyan/amber/pink).

## Steps
1. Subscribe to `useStreamStats()`.
2. Render numeric rows + mini-graphs.
3. Add reset button (clears ring buffer).
4. Render at LOW priority (1Hz refresh).

## Invariants
- 1Hz refresh max (no per-frame re-render).
- Mini-graphs share Canvas pool from S03-T04.
- Labels uppercase abbreviated.
